      <title>拜登和特朗普之间的辩论预计将是对能力和性格的考验</title>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/2024/06/27/g-s1-6676/debate-between-biden-and-trump-is-expected-to-be-a-test-of-competence-and-character</link>
